Sentencas: A new honeycomb-shaped La0.5Sr0.5Fe0.9P0.1O3-d (LSFP) material has been proposed as a cathode for proton-conducting solid oxide fuel cells (H-SOFCs).
Titulo: Bio-inspired honeycomb-shaped La0.5Sr0.5Fe0.9P0.1O3-das a high-performing cathode for proton-conducting SOFCs

Sentencas: Compared with conventional LSFP, the honeycomb-shaped does not change the crystal structure or the electronic structure of the material but offers a much higher surface area.
Titulo: Bio-inspired honeycomb-shaped La0.5Sr0.5Fe0.9P0.1O3-das a high-performing cathode for proton-conducting SOFCs

Sentencas: The unique honeycomb structure allows the easier diffusion of air and H2O evaporations in the cathode, thus benefiting the application of LSFP as a cathode for LSFP.
Titulo: Bio-inspired honeycomb-shaped La0.5Sr0.5Fe0.9P0.1O3-das a high-performing cathode for proton-conducting SOFCs

Sentencas: The honeycomb LSFP cathode's fuel cell shows a peak power density of 1474 mW cm(-2) at 700 (?)degrees C, which is higher than the conventional LSFP cell.
Titulo: Bio-inspired honeycomb-shaped La0.5Sr0.5Fe0.9P0.1O3-das a high-performing cathode for proton-conducting SOFCs

Sentencas: In addition, the fuel cell performance is also the highest ever reported for H-SOFCs based on the Sr-doped LaFeO3 (LSF) cathodes, making a new life for the first-generation LSF cathode for H-SOFCs.
Titulo: Bio-inspired honeycomb-shaped La0.5Sr0.5Fe0.9P0.1O3-das a high-performing cathode for proton-conducting SOFCs

Sentencas: The distribution of relaxation times (DRT) analysis for the cell reveals that the honeycomb-shaped cathode improves the oxygen reduction reaction (ORR) at the cathode, thus improving the cathode kinetics.
Titulo: Bio-inspired honeycomb-shaped La0.5Sr0.5Fe0.9P0.1O3-das a high-performing cathode for proton-conducting SOFCs
